人參與<br />\n3. 關心社會、陪審員、派傳單、放映會<br />\n4. <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">香城online有無限咁多職業</span></strong>，點解唔試多d呢，搵下邊個最岩心水（各有各做level up）或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾；Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.17 @Template End@"},{"pid":"6e658bacdd08982691a759a013920fe2778af61f","tid":1575934,"uid":270871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9866d8b443ba6b46280b467da650436880332dd7","tid":1575934,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T04:51:58.000Z","msg":"澳門狗冇資格說三道四 特別係嗰啲過氣內務長"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:06:27.000Z","msg":"一早做咗公廁ac啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72d032f3ca92248be11d056f5af82b913a8f58cf","tid":1575934,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:15:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"38f49ac38562f6fd000d29d081d32223c2ff57fd","tid":1575934,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:22:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"687119967ebff6ace28ce7dc2e17f2eee14b9b2b","tid":1575934,"uid":65439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:25:13.000Z","msg":"岩岩先有個鬧鳩連登仔打飛機輸哂既CNN post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位見到呢d負評再block就得<br />\n失敗悔氣主義post絕對會令士氣大降<br />\n唔輸都俾你講到輸 理得你幾有point"}]}